# 🚀 AI Job Search App – Semantic Search using Embeddings & ChromaDB

Excited to share a project I worked on 🚀  

As a **Brand Designer**, I contributed to the **UI/UX and visual identity** of an AI-powered Job Search application developed within my organization.

---

## 💡 What this application does

This application allows users to search for jobs using **natural language instead of traditional filters**.

Instead of manually selecting:
- Location  
- Salary  
- Job Role  

Users can simply type:

> “Nurse job in Croatia with good salary and accommodation”

The system understands the intent and returns the most relevant job results instantly.

---

## 🎯 How it works

- Job data is converted into **embeddings**
- Stored in a **vector database (ChromaDB)**
- User query is also converted into embeddings
- System performs **similarity search**
- Returns the most relevant job matches

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

- HuggingFace Embeddings  
- ChromaDB (Vector Database)  
- LangChain  
- Streamlit  

---

## 🎨 My Contribution (Brand Design)

- Designed a **premium SaaS-style UI**
- Created clean and modern layout
- Applied consistent **brand color system (Yellow & Blue)**
- Improved usability and visual hierarchy
- Focused on intuitive search experience

---

## 💡 Outcome

A smarter job search experience powered by AI:

- Faster than traditional filtering  
